data.description: Cute open floor plan on a quiet street in the Oakwood neighborhood. When you arrive at 1218 N 36th street, it automatically feels like home. You'll notice all new windows and fresh exterior paint. On the front of the property you have a private sitting area on the front porch and on the rear, you'll find a new wood deck perfect for entertaining. In the interior, there are refinished hardwood floors throughout, all new electrical fixtures, wiring, plugs and switches. The large bathroom has new penny tile flooring, tiled tub surround with niche and all new fixtures. Kitchen has double sink, gas range and refrigerator. Stackable washer and dryer convey. 9ft ceilings throughout! Home also has a new gas furnace and central air unit. And last but not least, a 2 car parking pad in the rear. Come see it SOON!
